{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c0586d445b","title":"答谢苏联军事顾问团祝贺我国国庆的复信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bfbd5f67e5","index":0,"year":1955,"month":10,"day":2,"articleId":"c0586d445b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"46d6705bec","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"肖向荣，当时任中共中央军委办公厅主任、国防部办公厅主任。"},{"id":"8aea0f82e1","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在肖向荣1955年9月30日给毛泽东的信上。肖向荣转交了苏联军事顾问团为祝贺我国国庆给毛泽东的信，并为毛泽东代拟了复信。"},{"id":"c60e30f902","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彼特鲁塞夫斯基，当时任苏联军事顾问团总顾问。彼得洛夫，当时任苏联军事顾问团政治处副主任。马里雅申，当时任苏联军事顾问团党组织书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a843d0fcba","type":"title","text":"答谢苏联军事顾问团祝贺我国国庆的复信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"46d6705bec","type":"paragraph","text":"退肖向荣”：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"8aea0f82e1","type":"subtitle","text":"照办。P","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"c60e30f902","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"3dbc82f779","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二日彼特鲁塞天斯基上将、彼得洛夫上校、马里雅申上校并转顾问团全体同志及其家属各同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"57d740aca6","type":"paragraph","text":"当我国六周年国庆之际，承赐祝贺，并表达良好的愿望，谨致深切的谢忧。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"cfc8326a73","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民革命的胜利和社会主义建设的成就，是和苏联共产党、苏联政府及所有在我国工作的苏联顾问、专家热情、无私的帮助分不开的。对此，中国人民将永志不忘","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"6b7f8c61c4","type":"paragraph","text":"祝彼特鲁塞天斯基顾问团在京专家及其家属的身体健康、愉快。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"8fec6d9a9d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"},{"id":"ef486ddccc","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年十月二日","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b"}],"page":{"id":"c5ab7d7fdc","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"c0586d445b","start":474,"end":475}}}},"__N_SSG":true}